# ROCm/HIP Research Library Inventory

upstream_repo: ROCm/hip
upstream_url: https://github.com/ROCm/hip
created_for: Netiv ROCN research library
branch: research/rocn-rocm-netiv-fork
status: staged research inventory
scope: root-level, docs root-level, include/hip root-level, cmake root-level, cmake/FindHIP root-level, bin root-level

This file is a research inventory for ROCN planning.
It is not a vendored copy of ROCm/HIP source.
It is not yet a full recursive manifest of the entire upstream repository.

FORMAT:
path | folder | kind | apparent purpose | ROCN relevance

================================================================================
ROOT FOLDERS
================================================================================
.azuredevops/ | / | folder | Azure DevOps CI configuration. | Low priority for ROCN; CI only.
.github/ | / | folder | GitHub repository metadata and workflow automation. | Low priority for ROCN; automation only.
.jenkins/ | / | folder | Jenkins CI support files. | Low priority for ROCN; CI only.
bin/ | / | folder | HIP command/tool helper scripts. | Medium priority; useful for future ROCN compiler-driver/tooling design.
cmake/ | / | folder | CMake integration and FindHIP/build support. | Medium priority; useful for future ROCN build adapter.
docker/ | / | folder | Docker/container build or test support. | Later priority; useful for reproducible ROCN test environments.
docs/ | / | folder | HIP documentation source. | High priority; best source for ROCN conceptual model.
include/ | / | folder | Public HIP include headers. | Highest priority; API surface to map into ROCN.

